(my average age has beenthirteen all my life). The cup of pleasure is brimming by now and before itspills I hasten to tiptoe across the bare parquet from my bed to hers. Herfair hair gets in the way of my kisses, but presently my lips find her cheekand neck, and her nightgown has buttons, and she says the maid has come intothe room, but it is too late, I cannot restrain myself, and the maid, abeauty in her own right, looks on, laughing.

